Limestone hills with primary and secondary lowland evergreen forests at elevations of 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF326A8DFEE59CCB1FB1B19C" box="[281,433,2705,2735]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.7" metricValueMax="9.7" metricValueMin="3.7" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" unit="m" value="670.0" valueMax="970.0" valueMin="370.0">370-970 m</quantity>
(
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF326A8DFE359CC91C48B19F" box="[457,584,2704,2733]" name="Vietnam" pageId="201" pageNumber="963">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
